&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Register your interest for future SDR roles at Prospa!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking to break into sales and grow your career in a supportive, high-energy environment? The &lt;strong&gt;Sales Development Representative (SDR) Team at Prospa&lt;/strong&gt; is the perfect place to start your journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be joining a collaborative, high-performing team that’s passionate about helping small businesses succeed. Along the way, you’ll sharpen your sales skills, gain hands-on experience, and have plenty of opportunities for career development and progression.&lt;/p&gt;
