&lt;li&gt;Understanding business owners’ needs and requirements while delivering exceptional customer service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with internal stakeholders to create value and achieve outstanding outcomes for Prospa and our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Having detailed conversations with business owners to drive commercial results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceeding key activity and performance metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
