&lt;li&gt;Detail-oriented with strong time management and organisational skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in fast-paced, high-volume phone-based customer service or sales roles is advantageous.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about supporting small businesses and a strong desire to learn and develop your career in sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
