&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifestyle&lt;/strong&gt;: Find your fit with flexible working options, top notch office facilities and diverse remote/ travel work options. You can also purchase additional leave and take up to 18 weeks paid parental leave.&lt;/li&gt;
